commit_message:
Messages can exist for 1 min after their TTL.

The relaxed TTL affects the following behaviors:

1. Get a specific message;
2. List messages;
3. Claim messages;
4. Queue stats of "free" messages.

Change-Id: I2bbadcfa8705dcb7d652f0d09e34bb8467298d8c
